      <title>[오늘의 날씨] 2024년 6월 5일</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2024/06/05/NNWL7PTKBNDLZEXMKTRZONVB4A/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2024/06/05/NNWL7PTKBNDLZEXMKTRZONVB4A/</guid>
